(5840, 2211, 702, 1, 'Star', '', '2008-06-13 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '', 'It’s a real sun……a real sun.\nI am waiting for……\nI am waiting for……\n\nIt’s a real sun……a real sun.\nI am waiting for……\nI am waiting for……\n\nI came to see the sunrise.\nI am waiting for……your candle and release.\n\nIt’s a fake sun without the glare……\nI came to see him.\n\nIt’s a real star……a real star.\n\nI am waiting for……\nI am waiting for……\n\nI came to see the glory.\nI am waiting for……the devil and fall.\n\nA…… one burning sun.\nA…… one changing star.', 162, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-06-13 18:06:20', '2015-03-12 13:33:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5841, 2211, 702, 2, '水鳥一號', '', '2008-06-13 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '', '眺望著遠方\n眼前是一片連著天閃著光 深藍色的海洋啊\n白色沙灘上 這裡有我的朋友和我的家\n現在我要離開它\n\n我轉頭看著那 那些曾經讓我成長陪我長大\n就像寶藏一樣的大自然\nI am flying, I can feel it.\n\n乘著夢飛翔\n跟著風天使和組先的翅膀 一起往溫暖的方向\n月亮在天上 星星陪著我整夜飛往希望\n朝向那新的天堂\n\n賤起一點水花 是那些海中的朋友道別的話\n祝福我們平安到達\n\nI am flying, I can feel it.\nThrough anything, no one can stop me.\n\nEvery day and every night\nWith my faith in the sky, light and dark tint all shine in my eyes.\nSo simple, so simple……\n\n乘著夢飛翔\n跟著風天使和祖先的翅膀 一起往溫暖的方向\n飛過了太陽\n海面在腳下閃著整片光芒 朝向那新的天堂\n\n沒有人能阻擋\n古老的記憶不會隨時間變化 永遠能飛向正確的地方\n\nI am flying, I can feel it.\nThrough anything, no one can stop me.\nEvery day and every night with my faith in the sky……', 296, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2008-06-13 18:09:14', '2015-03-12 13:33:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
